video_title: Be open to find new experiences #mindsetpodcast #motivation #lifechanging
transcript:
if you're unsure about your passion
doing the same things over and over
again won't bring you more clarity it's
not going to help you out and so what
you have to do is you have to experiment
you have to find new things you have to
take new routes you have to talk to new
people you have to try new hobbies you
have to cook new food eat new food
travel to different places and you have
to try to find new experiences
